data.description: DO NOT MISS THIS HOME! Seller is offering to pay the brand new solar off, and leave the brand new whole home Generac generator with a full price offer! That is over $60,000.00 in upgrades! WOW!!   The kitchen is a full remodel, with new cabinets and granite countertops. This spacious home boasts 5 bedrooms, 2.75 baths, a fully fenced and fully landscaped yard and new windows throughout the entire home. Enjoy the oversized back patio with power awning with LED lights and the concrete RV pad for your toys or trailer! This home is a one of a kind and has all the bells and whistles! Schedule a tour today!  Seller is also offering  a $5,000.00 total paint and carpet allowance to allow the buyers to make this home their very own!
